    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 7th level, you gain the ability to infuse arrows with magic. Whenever you fire a nonmagical arrow from a @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-items.REXaAPkxGwpNr8Dp]{Shortbow} or @Compendium[5e-complete.5e-items.nmd6Rsv5yqygkQ0w]{Longbow}, you can make it magical for the purpose of overcoming <strong>resistance</strong> and <strong>immunity</strong> to nonmagical attacks and damage. The magic fades from the arrow immediately after it hits or misses its target.</p>\n<section class=\"secret\">\n<p><em>Homebrew rule: Add +1 to damage to arrows effected by this ability.</em></p>\n</section>",
